* use Java coding conventions

* do not use abbreviations in names (variables, functions, files, etc.)

* always use braces:
  if(c) {
    then part
  } else {
    else part
  }

* use space between ')' and '{':
  %match(s) {
    p -> { ... }
  }

* use 2 spaces (not tabulation) for indenting

